      "text": "3. Abstract Factory Pattern -\n    a. It is a factory of factory. It is useful when a factory encapsulates another factory\n    b. If then else in a factory would only be applicable to the top most factory\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 23.368496859915542,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3. Abstract Factory Pattern -\n    a. It is a factory of factory. It is useful when a factory encapsulates another factory\n    b. If then else in a factory would only be applicable to the top most factory\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
