      "text": "OfficeBarista\n\ncached_coffee\nconstructor(coffee c)\nm_coffee = c\n\nprepareDripCoffee()\nif !cached_coffee\nreturn m_coffee.prepareDripCoffee\nelse\nreturn cached_coffee\n \n",
