      "originalText": "OfficeBarista\n\ncached_coffee\nconstructor(coffee c)\nm_coffee = new StarbucksBarista()\n\nprepareDripCoffee()\nif !cached_coffee\nreturn m_coffee.prepareDripCoffee\nelse\nreturn cached_coffee\n \n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
