      "updated": 1742400459097,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Client\n\n//prepare compositio\nAnimal D = new Dog()\nAnimal C = new Cat\nAnimal L = LandAnimal()\nL.add(D)\nL.add(C)\nAnimal E = new Eagle()\nAnimal C = new Crow()\nAnimal S = SkyAnimal()\nS.add(E)\nS.add(C)\nAnimal Main =\nAnimalComposition()\nMain.add(L)\nMain.add(S)\n\n//Calling makeSound\nMain.makeSound() // it\nwill traverse the tree.\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "lMnd9xy-aFuJgaRjal70u",
      "originalText": "Client\n\n//prepare compositio\nAnimal D = new Dog()\nAnimal C = new Cat\nAnimal L = LandAnimal()\nL.add(D)\nL.add(C)\nAnimal E = new Eagle()\nAnimal C = new Crow()\nAnimal S = SkyAnimal()\nS.add(E)\nS.add(C)\nAnimal Main = AnimalComposition()\nMain.add(L)\nMain.add(S)\n\n//Calling makeSound\nMain.makeSound() // it will traverse the tree.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
