    {
      "id": "UwgMEwKfiEdWTrd8O63xy",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 549.1048055327578,
      "y": 9416.842417765714,
      "width": 1739.4000244140625,
      "height": 212.77723692977355,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b4g",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1224060790,
      "version": 3123,
      "versionNonce": 223695158,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1742426613069,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "BEHAVIORAL PATTERNS\n\n1. Command Pattern -\n    a. It is a list of non-dependent concrete classes extending the same interface, with a common API called 'Execute'.\n       The Client simply iterate through the list of concrete classes and call the 'Execute' API.\n    b. It looks like an orchestrator/Facade Pattern where all the classes have the same interface, so we could just loop over it.\n    c. The difference between command and Facade pattern is that the latter have concrete classes where it does not extend the same interface.",
      "fontSize": 24.317398506259835,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "BEHAVIORAL PATTERNS\n\n1. Command Pattern -\n    a. It is a list of non-dependent concrete classes extending the same interface, with a common API called 'Execute'.\n       The Client simply iterate through the list of concrete classes and call the 'Execute' API.\n    b. It looks like an orchestrator/Facade Pattern where all the classes have the same interface, so we could just loop over it.\n    c. The difference between command and Facade pattern is that the latter have concrete classes where it does not extend the same interface.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Chs4dEsMQXwNAIXk6YxUM",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 551.8225333648649,
      "y": 9701.034310594918,
      "width": 364.6787136595466,
      "height": 410,
      "angle": 0,
