      "text": "ChainOfResponsibilityMiddleMan\n\ngetTopLevel\nCoffeeStep order = new\nCoffeeOrderStep()\n\nCoffeeStep prepare = new\nPrepareCoffeeStep()\n\nCoffeeStep deliver = new\nDeliverCoffeeStep()\n\norder.nextStep(prepare)\nprepare.nextStep(deliver)\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "7XSx-cN4ljH-FEkLa17BW",
      "originalText": "ChainOfResponsibilityMiddleMan\n\ngetTopLevel\nCoffeeStep order = new CoffeeOrderStep()\n\nCoffeeStep prepare = new PrepareCoffeeStep()\n\nCoffeeStep deliver = new DeliverCoffeeStep()\n\norder.nextStep(prepare)\nprepare.nextStep(deliver)\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
