      "text": "PrimeEligibilityVisitor\n\nacceptCloths(Product C)\nreturn C.getCatalog().size() >\n100\n\nacceptBooks(Product B)\nreturn B.getCatalog().size() >\n200\n\nacceptElectronics(Product E)\nreturn E.getCatalog().size() >\n50",
