      "originalText": "PrimeEligibilityVisitor\n\nacceptCloths(Product C)\nreturn C.getCatalog().size() > 100\n\nacceptBooks(Product B)\nreturn B.getCatalog().size() > 200\n\nacceptElectronics(Product E)\nreturn E.getCatalog().size() > 50",
