      "updated": 1742571514055,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\n5. Strategy Pattern -\n     a. The Client can select any one of the strategy to conduct operations on its object during runtime.\n     b. In the below example, client select Dumbell Strategy out of other options to perform his exercise.\n",
      "fontSize": 24.317398506259835,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\n5. Strategy Pattern -\n     a. The Client can select any one of the strategy to conduct operations on its object during runtime.\n     b. In the below example, client select Dumbell Strategy out of other options to perform his exercise.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
