      "text": "OrderMediator\nClient m_c\nBarista m_b\n\nsetBarista(Barista b)\nm_b = b\n\nplaceOrder(Client c, orderName)\nm_c = c\nm_b->prepareOrder(orderName)\n\nnotifyOrderReady(orderName)\nm_c->receiveOrder\n\n\n",
